{"tid":846118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視記者打人　中方：已無指控釋放　英警方：只是保釋　調查進行中","createTime":"2018-10-03T07:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T07:46:15.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"841e613e7df4aa732af8fed8de801ebd11e55a94","tid":846118,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.wenweipo.com/2018/10/02/IN1810020010.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2FIN1810020010.htm&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4aMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=2cddc701\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com/2018/10/02/IN1810020010.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【文匯網訊】中國中央廣播電視總台央視發言人1日晚間表示，中央電視台歐洲中心站記者孔琳琳已經獲釋，中央廣播電視總台向孔琳琳致以慰問。<br />\n<br />\n據中央電視台歐洲中心站通報，在我駐英使館的嚴正交涉和輿論壓力下，英國警方在短時間內釋放了孔琳琳。律師明確表示，孔琳琳是無指控釋放，其行為是正常履職，會議組織方舉止失當。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-45717070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-45717070&d=y20W634u0Ambr8VjUlsI4aMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=4f613ab3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-45717070&h=4f09808e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-45717070</a><br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會副主席羅傑斯反駁，指該名記者打人反而應該道歉，保守黨被問到會否道歉時回應稱，已經取消了有關人士會場的證件；警方表示該名女子涉嫌普通襲擊被捕，目前獲准保釋，但調查仍然進行中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DoXPoBxXUAAxNsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDoXPoBxXUAAxNsf.jpg&h=6980928f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93370e7a8deb313eb3c7b37613e0be3c34e9e2cf","tid":846118,"uid":18948,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"保守黨被問到會否道歉時回應稱，已經取消了有關人士會場的證件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c410fda7bbbc06e05b5e79c4a273c7c5a9709d4b","tid":846118,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/153704_b6a74b597438b21c4589da8f7c54f322.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F153704_b6a74b597438b21c4589da8f7c54f322.png&h=00530ca5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b26ed6e19ff6d1f197f5d1f3739d6989a53aa1a4","tid":846118,"uid":24730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">律師明確表示，孔琳琳是無指控釋放，其行為是正常履職，會議組織方舉止失當。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係支那律師定係英國執葉律師？"},{"pid":"4205e6ee66e753a3030fd698363ae9b5c9730fd1","tid":846118,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"打人仲要人道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253405c57b48ad06f67d426ab6b9d98c6cd0f73a","tid":846118,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:46:15.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，咁都放"}]}